        "title": "\u0130zmir_Water_Amount",
        "subtitle": "\u0130zmir ili baraj doluluk oran\u0131 ve su miktar\u0131 tahminine y\u00f6nelik ge\u00e7mi\u015f 10 y\u0131l",
        "description": "## \ud83d\udcc4 A\u00e7\u0131klama\n\nBu veri seti, \u0130zmir iline ait **2015\u20132024** y\u0131llar\u0131 aras\u0131ndaki ayl\u0131k baraj doluluk oran\u0131 (**DolulukOrani_Yuzde**) ve barajlardaki su miktar\u0131 (**SuDurumu_m3**) verilerini i\u00e7ermektedir.  \n\nVeriler; **\u0130ZSU (\u0130zmir Su ve Kanalizasyon \u0130daresi)** ve **T\u00dc\u0130K (T\u00fcrkiye \u0130statistik Kurumu)** kaynaklar\u0131ndan derlenmi\u015f, ek olarak:\n- N\u00fcfus\n- Ortalama s\u0131cakl\u0131k\n- Ya\u011f\u0131\u015f\n- Ayl\u0131k su t\u00fcketimi\n- Ayl\u0131k su \u00fcretimi\n- Turist say\u0131s\u0131 \n\nbilgilerini de kapsamaktad\u0131r.  \n\nBu s\u00fcr\u00fcm, modelleme s\u00fcrecinde **mevsimsel \u00f6zellikler**, **lag (\u00f6nceki ay)** ve **rolling (3 ayl\u0131k ortalama)** de\u011fi\u015fkenleri eklenmeden \u00f6nceki **hamla\u015ft\u0131r\u0131lm\u0131\u015f** veridir.  \n\n**Kullan\u0131m Alanlar\u0131:**\n- \ud83d\udcc8 Zaman serisi analizi\n- \ud83d\udd0d Regresyon tabanl\u0131 tahmin modelleri\n- \ud83c\udf26 Mevsimsellik ve iklim etkilerinin incelenmesi\n- \ud83d\udca7 Su kaynaklar\u0131 y\u00f6netimi senaryo \u00e7al\u0131\u015fmalar\u0131\n\n\n=== About this file ===\n\nAbout this file\n\ud83d\udcc2 Dosya Bilgisi\nDosya ad\u0131:\nmodellemeson.csv\nBoyut:\n~KB seviyesinde\nSat\u0131r say\u0131s\u0131:\n120\nS\u00fctun say\u0131s\u0131:\n9\nFrekans:\nAyl\u0131k veriler (2015\u20132024, 10 y\u0131l x 12 ay)\n\n\n=== Columns & descriptions ===\n\nTarih: Ayl\u0131k tarih bilgisi (YYYY-MM-DD format\u0131nda, her ay\u0131n ilk g\u00fcn\u00fc)\nDolulukOrani_Yuzde: Baraj doluluk oran\u0131 (%)\nSuDurumu_m3: Barajlardaki toplam su miktar\u0131 (m\u00b3)\nNufus: \u0130zmir ili toplam n\u00fcfusu (y\u0131ll\u0131k, t\u00fcm aylara ayn\u0131 de\u011fer yans\u0131t\u0131l\u0131r)\nSicaklik_Ort: Ayl\u0131k ortalama s\u0131cakl\u0131k (\u00b0C)\nYagis_mm: Ayl\u0131k toplam ya\u011f\u0131\u015f miktar\u0131 (mm)\nSu_Tuketim_Aylik_m3: Ayl\u0131k toplam su t\u00fcketimi (m\u00b3)\nURETIM_MIKTARI: Ayl\u0131k toplam su \u00fcretimi (m\u00b3)\nTurist_Sayisi: Turist say\u0131s\u0131(y\u0131ll\u0131k, t\u00fcm aylara ayn\u0131 de\u011fer yans\u0131t\u0131l\u0131r)\n",
